00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:29.100
And I'm talking about
when I've worked

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:31.630
and before that a little
less consciously--

00:02:31.630 --> 00:02:34.620
I hadn't really developed this
idea of creative trespassing.

00:02:34.620 --> 00:02:36.990
But when I was
bagging groceries,

00:02:36.990 --> 00:02:39.030
when I worked at
it as a barista,

00:02:39.030 --> 00:02:43.630
when I worked in a museum,
when I worked in technology.

00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:47.040
And, as I got more conscious
about this infusing imagination

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:50.490
