in order to be uniquely

00:03:01.410 --> 00:03:03.000
creative within our work.

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:04.620
And the second
thing that I learned

00:03:04.620 --> 00:03:07.350
is that if we bring
imagination to confront

00:03:07.350 --> 00:03:11.610
our self-limiting beliefs,
obstacles, everyday challenges,

00:03:11.610 --> 00:03:15.750
that we will experience
unlimited solutions, ideas,

00:03:15.750 --> 00:03:17.040
and innovations.

