That's Italian for conversation.

00:22:57.170 --> 00:23:00.605
So, we're just going to take
a moment to close our eyes,

00:23:00.605 --> 00:23:02.980
and I'm going to lead you
through a very short mind's eye

00:23:02.980 --> 00:23:03.502
journey.

00:23:03.502 --> 00:23:05.710
If you've not done a mind's
eye journey, all it means

00:23:05.710 --> 00:23:08.570
is that I will gently guide
you, and you just receive.

00:23:08.570 --> 00:23:09.070
That's it.

00:23:11.870 --> 00:23:17.890
So, I want you to imagine one
of your self-limiting beliefs.

00:23:17.890 --> 00:23:20.560
And, by that, I mean
a belief that you

00:23:20.560 --> 00:23:27.100
hold that stops you from having
and experiencing more joy, more

00:23:27.100 --> 00:23:31.470
creativity, and
pursuing your dreams.

00:23:31.470 --> 00:23:38.160
So, it could be anything from,
I don't deserve a raise to,

00:23:38.160 --> 00:23:42.950
I can't call myself an artist,
or I don't belong here.

00:23:50.700 --> 00:23:53.780
So, see this
self-limiting belief.

00:23:53.780 --> 00:23:56.930
I want you to gently let it go.

00:24:11.840 --> 00:24:14.190
And when you feel like
you've let it go--

00:24:14.190 --> 00:24:16.240
and this is a longer
process than just now--

00:24:16.240 --> 00:24:18.310
but when you've
let it go for now,

00:24:18.310 --> 00:24:19.660
I want you to open your eyes.

00:24:38.012 --> 00:24:40.520
OK.

00:24:40.520 --> 00:24:43.960
And now that you've
let something go,

00:24:43.960 --> 00:24:45.133
there's room to take a leap.

00:24:45.133 --> 00:24:46.300
So, we're going to stand up.

00:24:54.380 --> 00:24:57.910
And this isn't a big,
performative gesture.

00:24:57.910 --> 00:25:00.640
The most important part
about taking a leap

00:25:00.640 --> 00:25:02.450
is that we're doing it together.

00:25:02.450 --> 00:25:05.570
And so, it's-- bend your
knees just a little bit,

00:25:05.570 --> 00:25:06.370
just slightly.

00:25:06.370 --> 00:25:08.660
And, again, it's
not about jumping

00:25:08.660 --> 00:25:10.900
highest, it's just about--

00:25:10.900 --> 00:25:14.440
we didn't sign any waivers.

00:25:14.440 --> 00:25:16.720
This is a gentle jump.

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:19.400
Again, the most important part
is that we do it together.

00:25:19.400 --> 00:25:21.560
So, I'm going to count--
on the count of three,

00:25:21.560 --> 00:25:25.050
we're going to gently take
a leap of faith together.

00:25:25.050 --> 00:25:30.400
OK-- one, two, three.

00:25:30.400 --> 00:25:31.840
Awesome.

00:25:31.840 --> 00:25:33.280
Thank you so much.

00:25:33.280 --> 00:25:34.408
I appreciate it.

