00:26:06.780 --> 00:26:08.670
And you can also
remember that when you're

00:26:08.670 --> 00:26:10.328
leaping into the unknown--

00:26:10.328 --> 00:26:12.120
when you're starting
a new job, when you're

00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:15.150
tackling a new project, when
